Great in every way
I would rate Halong Bay as one of THE places to go to. The only slight downside was the weather which was overcast all day.
The islands you visit, the activities, the food were all excellent.
The area closed to tourism the day after our visit as a precaution against the virus so at the time of writing our boat was the last visit from any tourists anywhere. Let's hope it re-opens in the not so distant future.
